# Phase 12: Core Launcher Fixes & Logic Optimization

This phase addresses the critical feedback that the launcher fails at its basic tasks: categorizing resources, downloading the game, and launching it.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - We are changing the [LaunchService](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Services/LaunchService.cs#12-184) to handle modern asset indices dynamically.
> - We are moving `HasActiveTasks` from the UI code-behind to the [DownloadManagerService](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Services/Network/DownloadManagerService.cs#33-40) to fix the missing floating button.

## Proposed Changes

### 1. Resource Categorization (Fix "加进去啊")
#### [MODIFY] [ResourcesPage.xaml](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Views/ResourcesPage.xaml)
- Bind `RadioButton.IsChecked` to `SelectedCategory` using a new `StringMatchToBoolConverter` to ensure the sidebar UI accurately reflects the active category.

#### [MODIFY] [ResourcesViewModel.cs](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/ViewModels/ResourcesViewModel.cs)
- Ensure [SwitchCategory](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/ViewModels/ResourcesViewModel.cs#69-77) command properly triggers property changes and reloads content.

### 2. Download Manager & Floating Button
#### [MODIFY] [DownloadManagerService.cs](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Services/Network/DownloadManagerService.cs)
- Add `HasActiveTasks` property (computed) with `[NotifyPropertyChangedFor(nameof(HasActiveTasks))]` on `ActiveTasks` updates.
- Improve [ReplaceSource](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Services/Network/DownloadManagerService.cs#244-275) to handle more Mojang subdomains and ensure BMCLAPI assets structure is 100% correct.
- Fix a potential bug where the task collection wasn't causing the UI to update the button visibility.

### 3. Game Launching Fix (Fix "启动游戏还报错")
#### [MODIFY] [LaunchService.cs](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Services/LaunchService.cs)
- Replace hardcoded `"legacy"` asset index with dynamic resolution from the version JSON.
- Improve argument string building for modern versions (1.13+).
- Ensure `natives` path is correctly set for modern versions.

### 4. Download Service Stability
#### [MODIFY] [DownloadService.cs](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Services/Network/DownloadService.cs)
- Add more robust error catching in [DownloadBatchAsync](file:///C:/Users/Linyizhi/.gemini/GeminiLauncher/Services/Network/DownloadService.cs#156-208) to ensure one failed library doesn't stop the UI progress reporting, but reports the error to the task object.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- `dotnet build` to verify syntax.
- Mock a launch command to verify the generated arguments in `debug_launch_cmd.txt`.

### Manual Verification
- Start a download of a modern version (e.g. 1.20.1) and check if the floating button appears.
- Ensure clicking the button opens the dedicated manager.
- Verify game starts and doesn't crash due to missing assets/libraries.
